  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is a multicentre, open, uncontrolled trial for the observation of histological
      changes in breast fibroadenoma following high intensity focused ultrasound (HIFU).

      This study will be conducted in France in 20 patients with breast fibroadenoma with
      indication for a surgical resection. The patient will receive an HIFU treatment and 6 months
      after treatment, the need of the surgery is evaluated.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
